{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"41757-look-up","title":"Lève le nez!","description":"Des oiseaux, des chauves-souris, des avions, des cerfs-volants... T'arrive-t-il d'explorer le monde merveilleux au-dessus de nos têtes? Amuse-toi à repérer les choses bizarres dans ce petit livre sur les formes.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Aditi Dilip"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/41757-look-up"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714197/size3/b769676c4189b596ea7f2c7e00825ca4.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714197/size6/b769676c4189b596ea7f2c7e00825ca4.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58451/size6/d796f8a772546117127ab7f847c014c6.jpg","text":"Dans le ciel du matin,\nles oiseaux ont faim.\ntrouve celui qui a attrapé\nun ver pour son petit-déjeuner!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58439/size6/b7f72bcd3edfa61074cae8e504cdc384.jpg","text":"3/23","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58775/size6/249b5a7e0da8e234eaaf21cb6305e8a0.jpg","text":"Les papillons de toutes les couleurs,\nvolètent de fleurs en fleurs.\nMais il y en a un qui sort du lot,\ncar il n'a qu'une couleur sur le dos.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58440/size6/b75257a2d8e32cbd7ded615f88b043f0.jpg","text":"5/23","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58416/size6/79101d77b5b8d20dd443ee03b1160161.jpg","text":"Oh, le joli bouquet de cerfs-volants,\nqui dans les airs voltigent gaiement.\nL'un d'entre-eux est différent,\npeux-tu le repérer aisément?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58441/size6/1de7fde397f495b8330bb134ad565329.jpg","text":"7/23","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58417/size6/92be7a9825846259c6632ac89e40ae77.jpg","text":"Des grands et des petits carrés,\nsont les formes ici représentées.\nUne grille est autrement dessinée,\nMais où est-elle dissimulée?","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58442/size6/cd5d459877df1aa2afdbf62b98738622.jpg","text":"9/23","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58776/size6/14ec86ac3abb2524bd9f4dbd5250e2a9.jpg","text":"Au milieu des feuilles vertes,\nde ce vieil arbre, immense et inerte,\nse trouve une petite tache colorée.\nSeras-tu capable de la repérer?","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58443/size6/dc20e286430fba9158773cd273a99ff8.jpg","text":"11/23","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58420/size6/ece4d86dfab2853deaa87f25328ff863.jpg","text":"Plusieurs avions dans les cieux,\nlaissent une traînée blanche derrière eux.\nSauf pour l'un d'entre-eux,\nqui dessine des traits curieux.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58444/size6/9e8baab82c42021785a9a052fd511670.jpg","text":"13/23","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58421/size6/6bba366ae51123b025be9b4a03287cfe.jpg","text":"Des oiseaux pépient de bon \ncœur,\nsur un fil suspendu en hauteur.\nL'un d'eux est calme et immobile.\nQuel est donc ce petit volatile?","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58445/size6/abb8ea69be8b916b45a0b29467c0be08.jpg","text":"15/23","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58422/size6/7400b185cf41891711ee6a39846fdf8f.jpg","text":"Un petit groupe de nuages blancs,\nbrille par une belle journée d'été.\nL'un d'eux décide de faire tomber la pluie,\nTant pis pour ce que diront ses amis.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58446/size6/a89eda17e10386d1e9e9c64213528b14.jpg","text":"17/23","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58423/size6/daeb7a5636c2e5bcb372598dbf8599e1.jpg","text":"La journée est finie,\nplace désormais à la nuit.\nParmi toutes les lumières,\nl'une brille comme l'astre solaire.","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58447/size6/ba57fdfdd97a63076d7c6ea37f27bcfb.jpg","text":"19/23","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58424/size6/741ec2c4843ebfeed91476980747fd20.jpg","text":"Les chauves-souris dorment quand le soleil luit,\net se réveillent à la tombée de la nuit.\nPeux-tu repérer le petit individu bizarre,\nqui dort encore quand il fait noir?","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58448/size6/45567e9fdba562f8d5be653cabb257b8.jpg","text":"21/23","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58425/size6/f7c91870e9bad05ef2da7eeca56c9753.jpg","text":"L'univers contient des planètes,\nqui brillent tout là-haut.\nRepère celle qui est parfaite,\ncar elle possède un anneau.","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58450/size6/0fcc216029c652a8f0ccb9ad98fbe591.jpg","text":"23/23","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":22,"words":259}}